company.description:
At CSM Ingredients, we are a global ingredient-tech platform collaboratively enabling the evolution of taste and nutrition for the future of food’s ecosystem. Rooted in purpose coupled with more than a century of heritage and multi-sector professional know-how, since day one our work has extended beyond our core product offerings and services. We “Thrive for Impact,” aim to generate net positive impact, and take great pride in being active players in the visionary movement that is helping make the food industry’s transformation a reality.

We pair specialized technical expertise with world-class research and innovation excellence, working tirelessly to identify new and existing opportunities based on emerging and growing trends through open innovation. As a result, we are trusted partners who tailor effective, quality solutions for both the traditional and new food segments.
